💻 Mini Project – Remote Backup

Create remote-backup.sh

#!/bin/bash

REMOTE="ubuntu@192.168.1.100"

DEST="/home/ubuntu/backups"

FILE="/etc/hosts"

scp "$FILE" "$REMOTE:$DEST"

echo "Backup completed."
